10:T455,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TVSeries","name":"SK8 the Infinity","description":"Reki, a high school sophomore and skater, is addicted to “S,” a highly secret and dangerous downhill skateboarding race that takes place in an abandoned mine. The skaters are especially wild about the “beefs,” or heated battles that erupt in the races.<br>\n<br>\nReki takes Langa, a transfer student returning to Japan after studying abroad, to the mine where the races are held. Langa, who has no skateboarding experience, finds himself pulled into the world of “S”...<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Aniplex of America)\n<br><br>\n<i>Note: On March 13, 2021 a recap episode (9.5) went on air, postponing the broadcast of the regular episodes by one week.</i>","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx124153-uEBI764OSavB.png","datePublished":"2021-01-10","numberOfEpisodes":12,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","inLanguage":"ja","genre":["Action","Drama","Sports"],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":7.9,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":0}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"af7213d5-4485-4faa-a371-d1fb3af43cfe","tmdb_id":124153,"imdb_id":null,"content_type":"anime","title":"SK8 the Infinity","original_title":"SK∞ エスケーエイト","overview":"Reki, a high school sophomore and skater, is addicted to “S,” a highly secret and dangerous downhill skateboarding race that takes place in an abandoned mine. The skaters are especially wild about the “beefs,” or heated battles that erupt in the races.<br>\n<br>\nReki takes Langa, a transfer student returning to Japan after studying abroad, to the mine where the races are held. Langa, who has no skateboarding experience, finds himself pulled into the world of “S”...<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Aniplex of America)\n<br><br>\n<i>Note: On March 13, 2021 a recap episode (9.5) went on air, postponing 